body.value:
Dutch Foundations was established in 1989 in Abu Dhabi. Since that time the company has continued to grow and expand. Today, Dutch Foundations is a full-service ground engineering company with projects in most of the GCC countries and with independently managed, fully operational sister companies in Dubai, Iraq, Oman and Qatar.

Their work record includes over 4,000 projects, completed with great efficiency and quality workmanship. The rate of their substantial ongoing growth and growing list of satisfied clients attest to their devotion to excellence, which has helped them become one of the leading ground engineering and construction companies in the GCC.
